// Vim-style hjkl navigation. Additive: gitui's default arrow keys still work,
// and context-scoped letter bindings (e.g., `l` for stash_open in the stash
// tab) keep working since gitui resolves bindings by context.
(
    move_left:  Some(( code: Char('h'), modifiers: "" )),
    move_down:  Some(( code: Char('j'), modifiers: "" )),
    move_up:    Some(( code: Char('k'), modifiers: "" )),
    move_right: Some(( code: Char('l'), modifiers: "" )),
)
